    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1938-09-17T23:59:59-05:00"
                frus:doc-dateTime-min="1938-09-17T00:00:00-05:00" n="704"
                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d704">
                <note rend="inline" type="source">882.635 Neep/131</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The Minister in Liberia</hi> (<persName type="from">
                        <hi rend="italic">Walton</hi>
                    </persName>) <hi rend="italic">to the Chief of the Division of Near Eastern
                        Affairs</hi> (<persName type="to">
                        <hi rend="italic">Murray</hi>
                    </persName>)</head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Extract]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Monrovia</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1938-09-17">September 17,
                            1938</date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>
                    <hi rend="smallcaps">Dear Mr. Murray</hi>: …</p>
                <p>I have taken up with the President the suggestion you were good enough to make in
                    your communication of May 14. He received same with appreciation but thought as
                    there were no disputes, and that all commitments were being kept, it would be
                    inadvisable to enter into a formal discussion relative to same. In other words,
                    any movement initiated by him at this time might provoke unnecessary
                    agitation.</p>
                <p rend="center">. . . . . . . . . . . . . .</p>
                <p>Sincerely yours,</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Lester A. Walton</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
